{"sta":1,"data":{"subTitle":"百分比布局","content":"<p>某个网格的宽度为固定的百分比，其余网格平均分配剩余的空间。<a href=\"/app/data/css3/flex/case/per.html\" target=\"_blank\">查看Demo</a></p><p><img src=\"/app/data/css3/flex/img/bg2015071322.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p>HTML代码如下。</p><pre><code><span><span><span>&lt;</span>div</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>Grid<span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n  <span><span><span>&lt;</span>div</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>Grid-cell u-1of4<span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>...<span><span><span>&lt;/</span>div</span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n  <span><span><span>&lt;</span>div</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>Grid-cell<span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>...<span><span><span>&lt;/</span>div</span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n  <span><span><span>&lt;</span>div</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>Grid-cell u-1of3<span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>...<span><span><span>&lt;/</span>div</span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span><span><span>&lt;/</span>div</span><span>&gt;</span></span></code></pre><pre><code><span>.Grid </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>display</span><span>:</span> flex<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span>\n\n<span>.Grid-cell </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>flex</span><span>:</span> 1<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span>\n\n<span>.Grid-cell.u-full </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>flex</span><span>:</span> 0 0 100%<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span>\n\n<span>.Grid-cell.u-1of2 </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>flex</span><span>:</span> 0 0 50%<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span>\n\n<span>.Grid-cell.u-1of3 </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>flex</span><span>:</span> 0 0 33.3333%<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span>\n\n<span>.Grid-cell.u-1of4 </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>flex</span><span>:</span> 0 0 25%<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span></code></pre>"}}